      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "麻奈さんと遙子ちゃん……なんだか",
      "startTime": 51.0363728208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_03-skr001.wav",
      "text": "今の私と琴乃ちゃんみたい",
      "startTime": 54.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうかもしれないわね。あの頃の麻奈ちゃんが",
      "startTime": 57.0218602183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_03-hrk007.wav",
      "text": "さくらちゃんで、あの頃の私が……琴乃ちゃん",
      "startTime": 61.3854873975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
